  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n@noman-land wrote: \r\n\r\nThese network selectors are checkboxes so they look like you should be able to multiselect. Since you can't multiselect here perhaps it should be radio buttons or a dropdown or something instead to avoid confusion?\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/43950339-5587729e-9c90-11e8-9122-9bb7cdc76024.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Profile \r\n- Show advanced settings, turn on dev mode and go to network options\r\n- Click add new network button   \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.25\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
